      "entity_id": null,
      "paper_id": "paper_1",
      "text_span_id": "case_overview_1",
      "text": "She completed a comprehensive 76\u2010gene germline genetic test, which revealed tumor protein p53 (TP53) likely pathogenic variant (LPV; c.716A>G; p.N239S).",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "extraction_method": "llm",
      "study_type": "case report",
      "eco_type": null,
      "source": "extracted"
    },
    {
      "id": "paper_1:genetics:2:llm",
      "class": "Evidence",
      "entity_id": null,
      "paper_id": "paper_1",
      "text_span_id": "genetics_2",
      "text": "When TP53 PVs/LPVs are identified in a comprehensive germline panel, this raises concern for Li\u2013Fraumeni syndrome (LFS).",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "extraction_method": "llm",
      "study_type": "case report",
      "eco_type": null,
      "source": "extracted"
    },
    {
      "id": "paper_1:genetics:3:llm",
      "class": "Evidence",
      "entity_id": null,
      "paper_id": "paper_1",
      "text_span_id": "genetics_3",
      "text": "In the field of medical genetics, constitutional mosaicism is defined as the existence of genetically distinct populations of cells originating during embryogenesis in an individual.",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "extraction_method": "llm",
      "study_type": "case report",
      "eco_type": null,
      "source": "extracted"
    },
    {
      "id": "paper_1:genetics:4:llm",
      "class": "Evidence",
      "entity_id": null,
      "paper_id": "paper_1",
      "text_span_id": "genetics_4",
      "text": "The same specific TP53 LPV (c.716A>G [p.N239S]) was detected in all three tumors.",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "extraction_method": "llm",
      "study_type": "case report",
      "eco_type": null,
      "source": "extracted"
    },
    {
      "id": "paper_1:surgery:1:llm",
      "class": "Evidence",
      "entity_id": null,
      "paper_id": "paper_1",
      "text_span_id": "surgery_1",
      "text": "The breast cancer risk for women with LFS/germline TP53 LPVs/PVs is 80%\u201390%, with most breast cancers occurring at a younger age.",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "extraction_method": "llm",
      "study_type": "case report",
      "eco_type": null,
      "source": "extracted"
    },
    {
      "id": "paper_1:surgery:2:llm",
      "class": "Evidence",
      "entity_id": null,
      "paper_id": "paper_1",
      "text_span_id": "surgery_2",
      "text": "Furthermore, malignant phyllodes breast tumors in women are associated with LFS.",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "extraction_method": "llm",
      "study_type": "case report",
      "eco_type": null,
      "source": "extracted"
    },
