  "notes": [
    "This case report describes a complex genetic evaluation involving mosaic TP53 pathogenic variant leading to Li-Fraumeni syndrome diagnosis",
    "The patient had multiple breast tumors (bilateral DCIS and malignant phyllodes tumor) all harboring the same TP53 variant",
    "Cascade testing of parents was negative, but somatic testing of all three tumors confirmed mosaicism",
    "Management was significantly altered by genetic findings, leading to bilateral mastectomy instead of breast-conserving surgery"
  ]
